<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 100px;">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px;">
      <div>
        <h1 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
          🏹 <span>Barebow Training Tracker</span>
        </h1>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 4px;">String Walking Periodized Plan</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tabs -->
    <div class="training-tabs" id="trainingTabs">
      <button class="training-tab active" data-tab="today" onclick="switchTab('today')">📋 Today</button>
      <button class="training-tab" data-tab="week" onclick="switchTab('week')">📅 Week</button>
      <button class="training-tab" data-tab="stats" onclick="switchTab('stats')">📊 Stats</button>
      <button class="training-tab" data-tab="plan" onclick="switchTab('plan')">📖 Plan</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Tab Content -->
    <div class="training-content" id="tab-today"></div>
    <div class="training-content" id="tab-week" style="display:none;"></div>
    <div class="training-content" id="tab-stats" style="display:none;"></div>
    <div class="training-content" id="tab-plan" style="display:none;">
      <div class="t-card" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">🎯 Overview & Philosophy</h3>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li>Quality over quantity</li>
          <li>Track every session — arrows, scores, notes</li>
          <li>Warm-up 10-15 min before shooting</li>
          <li>Rest if form breaks down</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="t-card" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">🧵 String Walking Setup</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.6;">Use consistent tab marks for crawls. Arrow tip on gold, adjust fingers down the string for distance. Chart your crawls for: 10ft, 20yd, 30yd, 40yd, 55yd.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="t-card" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">📅 4-Week Periodized Schedule</h3>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li><strong>Week 1 (Base):</strong> Lower volume, technique focus</li>
          <li><strong>Weeks 2-3:</strong> Build volume</li>
          <li><strong>Week 4:</strong> Taper or maintain</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <p style="font-weight: 600;">Sample Weekly Schedule (4-5 shooting days):</p>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li><strong>Monday:</strong> Technique — 150-250 arrows</li>
          <li><strong>Wednesday:</strong> Scoring — 120-200 arrows</li>
          <li><strong>Friday:</strong> Volume — 180-300 arrows</li>
          <li><strong>Saturday:</strong> Long Session — 200-350 arrows</li>
          <li><strong>Tue / Thu / Sun:</strong> Rest or S&C</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="t-card" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">💪 Strength & Conditioning (2-3x/week)</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Warm-up: March in place, arm circles</p>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li>Bodyweight Squats</li>
          <li>Wall Angels</li>
          <li>Superman Holds</li>
          <li>Plank</li>
          <li>Band Pull-Aparts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="t-card" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">🎯 Shooting Drills (20-50 arrows per drill)</h3>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li><strong>Drill 1 — Crawl Charting:</strong> Chart crawls for 10ft, 20yd, 30yd, 40yd, 55yd.</li>
          <li><strong>Drill 2 — Blank Bale Form:</strong> Shoot at close range (5-10ft), focus on release & anchor.</li>
          <li><strong>Drill 3 — Progressive Distance Walk:</strong> Start at 10ft, walk back to 55yd.</li>
          <li><strong>Drill 4 — 20yd Indoor Scoring:</strong> 5-arrow ends, competition style.</li>
          <li><strong>Drill 5 — Field Simulation:</strong> Mix distances 10ft-55yd in one session.</li>
          <li><strong>Drill 6 — Release Isolation:</strong> Slow motion release practice at anchor.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="t-card">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">🥗 Nutrition & Recovery</h3>
        <ul class="t-list">
          <li>Stay hydrated, eat balanced meals</li>
          <li>Sleep well — recovery is training</li>
          <li>Take full rest days seriously</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="t-card" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <h3 class="t-card-title">🎬 Video Library</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">Reference videos for drills, exercises, and technique. Tap to watch.</p>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          <h4 style="font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px;">🏹 String Walking & Drills</h4>
          <ul class="t-video-list">
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gy67VKxq3ck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">How to String Walk a Barebow — Jake Kaminski</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5oE6rS2hF4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Barebow String Walking Tutorial</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tHvS6ZdHBrM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jake Kaminski String Walk / Crawl Charting Drill</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kE3oEmD31WY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">String Walking Demo — Progressive Distance</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxJp-Eauwqq3mSEG6SMZ_r0v5RDjfr4tJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jake Kaminski Form Drills Playlist (Blank Bale & More)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@JakeKaminski" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jake Kaminski YouTube Channel — Full Library</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h4 style="font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px;">💪 Strength & Conditioning</h4>
          <ul class="t-video-list">
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aclHkVKqBbM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bodyweight Squats — Proper Form for Beginners</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M_ooIhKYs7c" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wall Angels Tutorial</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z6PJMT2y8GQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Superman Holds Demo</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pvIjsG5Svck" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plank for Beginners — Proper Form</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JObYtU7Y7ag" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Band Pull-Aparts Tutorial</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* ─── Training Tabs ─── */
.training-tabs {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.training-tab {
  padding: 12px 20px;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all var(--transition);
}

.training-tab:hover { color: var(--color-text); }
.training-tab.active { color: var(--color-accent-hover); border-bottom-color: var(--color-accent); }

/* ─── Training Cards ─── */
.t-card {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 20px;
}

.t-card-title {
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  color: var(--color-accent-hover);
}

.t-list { padding-left: 20px; }
.t-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; }

/* ─── Stats Grid ─── */
.t-stats-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.t-stat {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 20px;
}

.t-stat-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
.t-stat-value { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 4px; }
.t-stat-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
.t-green { color: var(--color-success); }
.t-accent { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }
.t-red { color: var(--color-error); }

/* ─── Day Card ─── */
.t-day {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: border-color var(--transition);
}

.t-day.t-today { border-color: var(--color-accent); }

.t-day-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
  transition: background var(--transition);
}

.t-day-head:hover { background: var(--color-surface-hover); }

.t-day-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.t-badge {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.t-type-badge {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  background: var(--color-border);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.t-day-progress {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}

.t-day-progress .pct { font-weight: 600; }
.t-day-progress .pct.complete { color: var(--color-success); }

.t-progress-bar {
  width: 60px;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.t-progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: width 0.3s;
}

.t-progress-fill.complete { background: var(--color-success); }

.t-day-body { padding: 0 20px 16px; display: none; }
.t-day.open .t-day-body { display: block; }

/* ─── Checklist ─── */
.t-checklist { list-style: none; }

.t-checklist li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.t-checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.t-checklist input[type="checkbox"] {
  appearance: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  min-width: 22px;
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-top: 1px;
  position: relative;
  transition: all var(--transition);
  background: transparent;
}

.t-checklist input[type="checkbox"]:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); }

.t-checklist input[type="checkbox"]:checked {
  background: var(--color-accent);
  border-color: var(--color-accent);
}

.t-checklist input[type="checkbox"]:checked::after {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--color-bg);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.t-item-text { flex: 1; }
.t-item-text.done { text-decoration: line-through; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
.t-item-cat { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-accent-hover); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.3px; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }

/* ─── Full-width progress bar ─── */
.t-full-progress {
  width: 100%;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 3px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.t-full-progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 3px;
  transition: width 0.3s;
}

/* ─── Bar Chart ─── */
.t-bar-chart {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  gap: 4px;
  height: 120px;
  padding-top: 8px;
}

.t-bar-col {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  height: 100%;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

.t-bar {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 36px;
  border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  min-height: 2px;
  transition: height 0.3s;
}

.t-bar.empty { background: var(--color-border); }
.t-bar-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .t-stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .training-tab { padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .arrow-counter-row { flex-direction: column; }
}

/* ─── Arrow Counter ─── */
.arrow-counter {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.arrow-counter-title {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.arrow-counter-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.arrow-count-display {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-text);
  min-width: 80px;
  text-align: center;
}

.arrow-btn {
  background: var(--color-surface-hover);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  color: var(--color-text);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  transition: all var(--transition);
  padding: 10px 16px;
}

.arrow-btn:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); background: var(--color-accent-light); }
.arrow-btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }

.arrow-btn.primary {
  background: var(--color-accent);
  border-color: var(--color-accent);
  color: var(--color-bg);
}

.arrow-btn.primary:hover { background: var(--color-accent-hover); }

.arrow-btn.danger {
  border-color: var(--color-error);
  color: var(--color-error);
}

.arrow-btn.danger:hover { background: var(--color-error-bg); }

.arrow-btn.finish {
  background: var(--color-success);
  border-color: var(--color-success);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  padding: 10px 20px;
}

.arrow-btn.finish:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

.arrow-finished {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  background: var(--color-success-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-success);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-success);
  margin-top: 12px;
}

.arrow-quick-add {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.arrow-custom-input {
  width: 70px;
  padding: 8px 10px;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  color: var(--color-text);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-family: var(--font-family);
  text-align: center;
}

.arrow-custom-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--color-accent); }

/* ─── Video List ─── */
.t-video-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.t-video-list li {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.t-video-list a {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  color: var(--color-text);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: background var(--transition);
}

.t-video-list a:hover {
  background: var(--color-surface-hover);
  color: var(--color-accent-hover);
}

.t-video-list a::before {
  content: '▶';
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  min-width: 28px;
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
}

/* ─── Inline Video Links (in checklists) ─── */
.t-inline-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  margin-left: 6px;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  background: var(--color-accent-light);
  color: var(--color-accent-hover) !important;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
  transition: all var(--transition);
}

.t-inline-link:hover {
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: var(--color-bg) !important;
}
</style>

